= NAME

dsck2mail - simple disck usage notifier via sendmail

= SYNOPSIS

((*dsck2mail*))

= DESCRIPTOIN

((*dsck2mail*)) was designed which is used with cron.
If dsck exit with alert, send it to root as mail.

= BUGS

((*dsck2mail*)) just exec sendmail. Thus, this will not work
when mail spool directory (e.g. /var) is completely full.
